{
  "stem": "935.9",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And then very slowly, I crawled on my hands and my knees and my belly, out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And the road was a disaster.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "We had lost so many people, so many wounded.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And the Germans who wanted to leave had left their little villages to get retreat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "They came over our dead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "They crawled over our dead into our cars, which were turned over, and stole the Red Cross packages which still were there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We didn't have enough trucks anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "There was no doctor, not even among the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "The generals kept saluting, saying how sorry they were, and it was awful.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "They tried to help as much to turn the trucks over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "We knew they would come back to finish the British [INAUDIBLE] not us, but them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And we had to get out of there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "While there were only less than half of our cars left, we brought whatever we could into the trucks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "We had to leave the wounded behind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "Of course the dead, but the wounded too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And then this was 20 kilometers to Lubeck, which is about, I don't know, 50 miles.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "Something like that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And you know, in Europe, you have-- every mile, you have a little stone where it says so and so many kilometers, so and so many kilometers.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "These 20 kilometers were the longest in the world.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "It was a country road.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "It was the end of April.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "Hot for this time of year.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "Unbelievably hot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "And it was, you know, one of those dusty country roads with ditches on both sides.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "And the truck was overloaded.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "And it went like a snail.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "Much too slow.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "And I kept counting the kilometers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "And it was bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "My lips were burnt, my tongue was on fire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "This was awful.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
